    "id": "the_lantern_wake_tavern",
    "name": "The Lantern & Wake Tavern",
    "description": "The Lantern & Wake is one of Brightvale's oldest and most beloved taverns, standing just a stone's throw from the harbor docks. Captains fresh from distant voyages share tables with local fishermen, while merchants haggle over contracts beside crackling hearthfires. The tavern's founder claimed that a lantern left burning in the upper window would always guide sailors safely home, and the tradition has been faithfully maintained for nearly two centuries.",
